
---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Projects | Handyman Cruz</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <main style="max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 1rem;">
      <h1 style="color: #007acc;">Services I Offer</h1>

      <section style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>General Repairs</h2>
        <p>Door fixes, drywall patching, fence repairs — quick, tidy, and done right.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Tiling & Grouting</h2>
        <p>Bathroom, kitchen, laundry. Precision tile laying, regrouting, and waterproofing.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Concreting & Paving</h2>
        <p>Driveway patch-ups, garden paving, or slab foundations. Functional and durable.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Flatpack Assembly</h2>
        <p>Desks, shelves, beds, and furniture built without the Allen key rage.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <h2>Custom Requests</h2>
        <p>If it’s hands-on and you need a reliable bloke to sort it — I’ll make it happen. Just ask.</p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>